dialog.body: Hello there! Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Sean Alexander. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Angela Johnson.
Great to meet you, Angela. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five zero three two one and my date of birth is December fifteenth nineteen eighty-four.
Thank you, Angela. One more piece of information required, could you provide your current address with the postal code, please?
Of course, my address is 123 Maple Street, Cityville, Postal Code: V1X 2Y7.
Thank you for providing the information, Angela. Is there anything specific you would like to address today regarding your policy or coverage?
I just wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Certainly, Angela. Let's discuss the details of the new vehicle you wish to add. Thank you for your time.
